high_descs: Turn around and walk forward then turn right and walk to the nearest sofa in the living room.
Pick up the newspaper from the sofa.
Turn left and walk to the dresser by the window.
Put the newspaper down on top of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the newspaper on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around then turn right towards the sofa in the hall.
Pick up the newspaper from the sofa.
Turn around and move to the dresser.
Place the newspaper on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Replace the Newspaper from Dresser to the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the newspaper from the couch.
Turn around and go near the dresser.
Put the newspaper on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Placed the newspaper on the Dresser.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the sofa.
Pick the newspaper from the sofa.
Turn left to reach the dresser.
Put the newspaper on the top of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the newspaper on the top on the dresser.
